            <title>[CAMEL-4264] The routeContext stack of DefaultUnitOfWork should be thread safe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-4264</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Here is the stack trace&lt;/p&gt;
